02:24.010 --> 02:28.174
<i>The patients are beginning to speak
of a presence in the clinic.</i>

02:28.982 --> 02:31.041
<i>Something they can feel.</i>

02:31.251 --> 02:33.344
<i>Something I can feel.</i>

02:33.553 --> 02:37.114
<i>Something I don't dare admit
I've felt before.</i>

02:40.560 --> 02:43.859
<i>While I continue to explain away
the Boogeyman's existence...</i>

02:44.063 --> 02:47.260
<i>...as nothing but the darkness
within ourselves...</i>

02:47.467 --> 02:49.196
<i>...I'm left to wonder...</i>

02:49.402 --> 02:52.235
<i>...does that make him anything less
than real?</i>

04:55.995 --> 04:57.394
